# WorkflowsSection Redesign - Implementation Plan

## 🎯 Current State Assessment

### Available Components
✅ **Existing Theater Components** (in `src/components/vue/views/home/workflows/`):
- `AIEnhancementTheater.vue` - AI content optimization animation
- `AnalyticsTheater.vue` - Real-time analytics dashboard animation
- `SchedulingTheater.vue` - Smart scheduling clock animation

✅ **Available UI Components** (in `src/components/vue/ui/`):
- `WorkflowHeroAnimation.vue` - Cross-platform publishing animation
- `OrbitingPlatforms.vue` - Platform orbit animation for CTA
- `CompletionAnimation.vue` - Success/completion animation

### Current WorkflowsSection Problems
❌ **6 text-heavy workflow cards** with static icons
❌ **No visual demonstrations** of actual workflow capabilities
❌ **Generic descriptions** that could describe any automation tool
❌ **Low engagement** - just cards sliding up on scroll
❌ **Doesn't showcase** the product's unique features

---

## 🎭 Redesign Strategy: 4 Visual Theaters

### Theater Mapping

| # | Theater Name | Component | Status | Location |
|---|-------------|-----------|--------|----------|
| 1 | Cross-Platform Publishing | `WorkflowHeroAnimation.vue` | ✅ Ready | `ui/` |
| 2 | AI Content Optimization | `AIEnhancementTheater.vue` | ✅ Ready | `workflows/` |
| 3 | Smart Scheduling | `SchedulingTheater.vue` | ✅ Ready | `workflows/` |
| 4 | Real-Time Analytics | `AnalyticsTheater.vue` | ✅ Ready | `workflows/` |

**CTA Section**: Use `OrbitingPlatforms.vue` as eye-catching background

---

## 📋 Implementation Steps

### Phase 1: Create Theater Shell Components (30 min)

**1.1 Create TheaterLabel.vue**
```vue
<!-- src/components/vue/ui/TheaterLabel.vue -->
