defineProps<{
  text: string
}>()
</script>

<style scoped>
.theater-caption {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: rgb(107 114 128);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 1rem auto 0;
}

:global([data-theme="dark"]) .theater-caption {
  color: rgb(156 163 175);
}
</style>
```

---

### Phase 2: Redesign WorkflowsSection.vue (2 hours)

**2.1 New Template Structure**
```vue
<template>
  <section id="workflows" class="py-28 md:py-36 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 relative z-10">

      <!-- Minimal Header -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-20 text-center mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <div class="h-10 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-500 to-accent-purple-500 rounded-full mr-4"></div>
          <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">
            See Workflows in Action
          </span>
        </div>
