  min-height: 400px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

/* Responsive adjustments */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .theater-stage {
    min-height: 300px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    min-height: 300px;
  }
}

/* Reduced motion support */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .theater-stage * {
    animation: none !important;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease !important;
  }
}
</style>
```

---

### Phase 3: Component Verification (1 hour)

**3.1 Check Theater Component Props**

Verify each theater component accepts the expected props:

```typescript
// AIEnhancementTheater.vue should have:
defineProps<{
  active: boolean
}>()

// SchedulingTheater.vue should have:
defineProps<{
  active: boolean
}>()

// AnalyticsTheater.vue should have:
defineProps<{
  active: boolean
}>()

// WorkflowHeroAnimation.vue should have:
defineProps<{
  autoplay?: boolean
}>()
```

**3.2 Test Animation Triggers**

Each theater should:
- ✅ Start animation when `active` prop becomes `true`
- ✅ Pause/reset when scrolled out of view
- ✅ Clean up intervals/timers on unmount
- ✅ Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`

---

### Phase 4: Mobile Optimization (1 hour)

**4.1 Responsive Stage Heights**
```css
/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .theater-stage {
    min-height: 280px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
}

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
  .theater-stage {
    min-height: 350px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .theater-stage {
    min-height: 450px;
    padding: 3rem;
  }
}
```

**4.2 Theater Spacing**
```css
.theater {
  margin-bottom: 3rem; /* Mobile */
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .theater {
    margin-bottom: 4rem; /* Desktop */
  }
}
```

---

### Phase 5: Performance Optimization (30 min)

**5.1 Lazy Loading**
- Use Astro's `client:visible` directive for all theater components
- Only start animations when theater is in viewport
- Pause animations when scrolled away

**5.2 Animation Cleanup**
Ensure each theater component has:
```typescript
import { onUnmounted, watch } from 'vue'

// Watch active prop
watch(() => props.active, (isActive) => {
  if (isActive) {
    startAnimation()
  } else {
    pauseAnimation()
  }
})

// Clean up on unmount
onUnmounted(() => {
  clearAllIntervals()
  cancelAnimations()
})
```

---

## ✅ Acceptance Criteria

### Visual Quality
- [ ] All 4 theaters render correctly on desktop
- [ ] Animations play smoothly (60fps target)
- [ ] No layout shifts during animations
- [ ] Glassmorphism effect works in light/dark mode
- [ ] Number badges have gradient and shadow

### Functionality
- [ ] Theaters activate when scrolled 30% into view
- [ ] Animations pause when scrolled away
- [ ] CTA section has OrbitingPlatforms background
- [ ] All animations respect reduced motion preference
- [ ] No console errors or warnings

### Responsive Design
- [ ] Mobile (< 640px): Compact stages, vertical layout
- [ ] Tablet (640-1023px): Medium stages, simplified animations
- [ ] Desktop (1024px+): Full animations, larger stages
- [ ] Touch targets are 44px+ on mobile

### Performance
- [ ] Lighthouse Performance score > 90
- [ ] No jank during scroll
- [ ] Components lazy load with client:visible
- [ ] Animations clean up properly
- [ ] Bundle size increase < 30kb

### Accessibility
- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG 2.2 AA
- [ ] Keyboard navigation works
- [ ] Screen readers can access content
- [ ] No flashing/strobing effects
- [ ] Focus indicators visible

---

## 🚀 Deployment Steps

1. **Create shell components** (TheaterLabel, TheaterCaption)
2. **Verify theater components** accept correct props
3. **Redesign WorkflowsSection.vue** with new structure
4. **Test on development server** (npm run dev)
5. **Mobile responsive testing** on real devices
6. **Performance audit** with Lighthouse
7. **Accessibility testing** with screen reader
8. **Create preview section** in index.astro (optional)
9. **Final QA** across browsers
10. **Deploy to production**

---

## 📊 Success Metrics

### Before Launch
- ✅ All 4 theaters working smoothly
- ✅ Mobile responsive across devices
- ✅ Lighthouse Performance > 90
- ✅ Zero console errors
- ✅ WCAG 2.2 AA compliant

### After Launch (2 weeks)
- 🎯 Time on page increase > 30%
- 🎯 Scroll depth to workflows > 80%
- 🎯 CTA click-through rate > 5%
- 🎯 Bounce rate decrease > 20%

---

## 🔧 Component Dependencies

### Required Imports
```typescript
// From VueUse
import { useElementVisibility } from '@vueuse/core'

// From Iconify
import { Icon } from '@iconify/vue'

// Theater Components
import WorkflowHeroAnimation from '@/components/vue/ui/WorkflowHeroAnimation.vue'
import AIEnhancementTheater from './workflows/AIEnhancementTheater.vue'
import SchedulingTheater from './workflows/SchedulingTheater.vue'
