**Center Grid** (unified feed):
```vue
<div class="unified-grid absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
    <div 
      v-for="(post, i) in unifiedPosts" 
      :key="i"
      class="post-card"
      :style="{ '--post-index': i, '--platform-color': post.color }"
    >
      <div class="w-full h-24 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg mb-2"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <Icon :icon="post.icon" :class="post.color" class="w-5 h-5" />
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-1">
          <div class="h-2 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded w-full"></div>
          <div class="h-2 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded w-2/3"></div>
        </div>
