    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
    Unified Feed
  </div>
</div>
```

**Flying Posts Animation**:
For each platform, create flying post cards that travel from corner to center:
```vue
<div
  v-for="(platform, i) in platforms"
  :key="`flying-${i}`"
  class="flying-post absolute"
  :class="platform.position"
  :style="{
    '--delay': `${i * 0.5}s`,
    '--start-x': getStartX(platform.position),
    '--start-y': getStartY(platform.position),
    '--platform-color': platform.color
  }"
>
  <div class="w-16 h-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border-2 p-2" 
       :style="{ borderColor: 'var(--platform-color)' }">
    <Icon :icon="platform.icon" :class="platform.color" class="w-6 h-6" />
  </div>
</div>
```

**Animations**:
```css
@keyframes fly-to-center {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
  }
  20% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(calc(var(--start-x) * -0.3), calc(var(--start-y) * -0.3)) scale(0.95);
  }
  80% {
    opacity: 0.8;
    transform: translate(calc(var(--start-x) * -0.9), calc(var(--start-y) * -0.9)) scale(0.6);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(var(--start-x), var(--start-y)) scale(0.3);
  }
}

.flying-post {
  animation: fly-to-center 2s ease-in-out var(--delay) infinite;
}

@keyframes post-card-appear {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.9);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1);
  }
}

.unified-posts-theater.is-active .post-card {
  animation: post-card-appear 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards;
