Create 2 new Social Hub theater animations showcasing unified content management features. Follow animation patterns from @src/components/vue/views/home/workflows/AIEnhancementTheater.vue.

**PHASE A: Create UnifiedPostsTheater.vue**

Location: `src/components/vue/views/home/workflows/UnifiedPostsTheater.vue`

**Concept**: Posts from 4 different platforms flow from corners and converge into a unified center grid.

**Component Structure**:
```typescript
interface Props {
  active: boolean
}

const props = defineProps<Props>()
const { optimizations } = useAnimationEnvironment()
const shouldAnimate = computed(() => props.active && !optimizations.reducedMotion)
```

**Layout**:
- Container: `h-96 relative w-full overflow-visible px-4`
- 4 platform icons at corners (position: absolute)
  - Top-left: Instagram (`mdi:instagram`, pink-600)
  - Top-right: Twitter (`mdi:twitter`, blue-500)
  - Bottom-left: Facebook (`mdi:facebook`, blue-600)
  - Bottom-right: LinkedIn (`mdi:linkedin`, blue-700)
- Center unified grid: 2x2 layout of post cards
- Flying post cards that travel from corners to center

**Platform Positions**:
```typescript
const platforms = [
  { name: 'Instagram', icon: 'mdi:instagram', color: 'text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400', 
    position: 'top-4 left-4' },
  { name: 'Twitter', icon: 'mdi:twitter', color: 'text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400', 
    position: 'top-4 right-4' },
  { name: 'Facebook', icon: 'mdi:facebook', color: 'text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400', 
    position: 'bottom-4 left-4' },
  { name: 'LinkedIn', icon: 'mdi:linkedin', color: 'text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-500', 
    position: 'bottom-4 right-4' }
]
```

**Center Grid** (unified feed):
```vue
<div class="unified-grid absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
    <div 
      v-for="(post, i) in unifiedPosts" 
      :key="i"
      class="post-card"
      :style="{ '--post-index': i, '--platform-color': post.color }"
    >
      <div class="w-full h-24 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg mb-2"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <Icon :icon="post.icon" :class="post.color" class="w-5 h-5" />
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-1">
          <div class="h-2 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded w-full"></div>
          <div class="h-2 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded w-2/3"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
    Unified Feed
  </div>
</div>
```

**Flying Posts Animation**:
For each platform, create flying post cards that travel from corner to center:
```vue
<div
  v-for="(platform, i) in platforms"
  :key="`flying-${i}`"
  class="flying-post absolute"
  :class="platform.position"
  :style="{
    '--delay': `${i * 0.5}s`,
    '--start-x': getStartX(platform.position),
    '--start-y': getStartY(platform.position),
    '--platform-color': platform.color
  }"
>
  <div class="w-16 h-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border-2 p-2" 
       :style="{ borderColor: 'var(--platform-color)' }">
    <Icon :icon="platform.icon" :class="platform.color" class="w-6 h-6" />
  </div>
</div>
```

**Animations**:
```css
@keyframes fly-to-center {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
  }
  20% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(calc(var(--start-x) * -0.3), calc(var(--start-y) * -0.3)) scale(0.95);
  }
  80% {
    opacity: 0.8;
    transform: translate(calc(var(--start-x) * -0.9), calc(var(--start-y) * -0.9)) scale(0.6);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(var(--start-x), var(--start-y)) scale(0.3);
  }
}

.flying-post {
  animation: fly-to-center 2s ease-in-out var(--delay) infinite;
}

@keyframes post-card-appear {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.9);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1);
  }
}

.unified-posts-theater.is-active .post-card {
  animation: post-card-appear 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards;
  animation-delay: calc(0.3s + var(--post-index) * 0.1s);
}
```

**Helper Functions**:
```typescript
const getStartX = (position: string) => {
  if (position.includes('left')) return '300px'
  if (position.includes('right')) return '-300px'
  return '0px'
}

const getStartY = (position: string) => {
  if (position.includes('top')) return '200px'
  if (position.includes('bottom')) return '-200px'
  return '0px'
}

const unifiedPosts = computed(() => [
  { icon: 'mdi:instagram', color: 'text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400' },
  { icon: 'mdi:twitter', color: 'text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400' },
  { icon: 'mdi:facebook', color: 'text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400' },
  { icon: 'mdi:linkedin', color: 'text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-500' }
])
```

